'''Jump''' was a short, spindly [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] and thug-for-hire who tried to seduce [[Salla Zend]] and wound up in a fight with her. During the fight, his shoulder was dislocated and he was helped out of the [[Blue Light]] tavern by a friend.

